<h2>Transaction Import Successful</h2>

<p>Hello {{userName}},</p>

<div class="alert alert-success">
    <h3>âœ… Import Completed Successfully</h3>
    <p>Your transaction import has been processed successfully.</p>
</div>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3>Import Summary</h3>
    <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
            <td>Import Type:</td>
            <td>{{importType}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>File Name:</td>
            <td>{{fileName}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Total Transactions:</td>
            <td>{{totalTransactions}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Successfully Imported:</td>
            <td>{{successfulImports}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Failed Imports:</td>
            <td>{{failedImports}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Import Date:</td>
            <td>{{formatDateTime importDate}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Processing Time:</td>
            <td>{{processingTime}} seconds</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

{{#if importNotes}}
<div class="alert alert-info">
    <h4>Import Notes</h4>
    <p>{{importNotes}}</p>
</div>
{{/if}}

{{#if failedTransactions}}
<div class="alert alert-warning">
    <h4>Failed Transactions</h4>
    <p>The following transactions could not be imported:</p>
    <ul>
        {{#each failedTransactions}}
        <li>{{description}} - {{reason}}</li>
        {{/each}}
    </ul>
</div>
{{/if}}

<div class="alert alert-info">
    <h4>Next Steps</h4>
    <ol>
        <li>Review the imported transactions in the system</li>
        <li>Verify data accuracy and completeness</li>
        <li>Process any reconciliation tasks if needed</li>
        <li>Contact support if you notice any discrepancies</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<p>You can view the imported transactions in the SDK Admin Portal under the Transactions section.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
<strong>SDK Admin Portal Team</strong></p> 